data.description: This well-maintained home is conveniently located in the Stone Oak area, with easy access to 281 and 1604. The lower level boasts a large living/dining combo, and a separate family room with a stylish custom fireplace that connects to the eat-in kitchen with wrap-around bar. The second level includes the master bedroom, two additional bedrooms, and a loft with two separate areas that overlook the living area.
